# Helmfile Deployment

Helmfile for managing Redis and microservices Helm charts.

## Prerequisites

- helmfile installed
- kubectl configured
- Helm 3.0+

## Deploy All
```bash
cd helmfile
helmfile sync
```

## Deploy Specific Release
```bash
helmfile -l name=redis sync
helmfile -l name=microservices sync
```

## Environments

Development:
```bash
helmfile -e dev sync
```

Production:
```bash
helmfile -e prod sync
```

## List Releases
```bash
helmfile list
```

## Diff Before Apply
```bash
helmfile diff
```

Note: Requires helm-diff plugin:
```bash
helm plugin install https://github.com/databus23/helm-diff
```

## Destroy
```bash
helmfile destroy
```

## Structure

- `helmfile.yaml` - Main configuration
- `values/` - Values files per chart
- `environments/` - Environment-specific overrides
- `.env.example` - Environment variable template